//Previous interventions / therapies - Fine needle aspiration


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Mammography/Breast ultrasound
When I select 'Yes' radio button
Then 'Add new finding' button is disabled
When I select 'Yes' radio button
Then 'Previous interventions / therapies' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Fine needle aspiration' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
And single choice Localizer is enabled
When I select 'Right lower outer quadrant' on the Localizer
Then 'Right upper lower quadrant' part turns red
When I select 'Right upper outer quadrant' on the Localizer
Then 'Right upper outer quadrant' part turns red
And 'Right upper lower quadrant' part turns is automatically deselected and turns white
When I select 'Left lower inner quadrant' on the Localizer
Then 'Left lower inner quadrant' turns red
And 'Right upper outer quadrant' is automatically deselected and turns white
